<h2 id="step-3-install-the-package-with-pip">Step 3: Install the Package
with Pip</h2>
<p>The general format is
<code>pip install git+[repository_url]@[version_specifier]</code>. The
version specifier can be a branch name, tag, or commit hash.</p>
